.SH DIAGNOSTICS
.sp
.LP
In addition to being logged, the following messages can appear on the system console. All messages are formatted in the following manner: 
.sp
.in +2
.nf
Warning: <device path> (usb_ac<instance num>): Error Message...
.fi
.in -2
.sp

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fBFailure to plumb audio streams drivers.\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
The \fBusb\fR audio streaming driver or the \fBhid\fR driver could not be plumbed under the audio control driver and the device is not usable.
.RE

